    positive integers that start or end with 1.
    """
    # A positive n-digit integer ranges from 10^n - 1 to 10^n
    # The count of 1-digit positive integers (1-9) is 9.
    # The count of n-digit numbers is: 10^{n-1} (numbers that are not n-digit).
    # The count of 1-n digit numbers that start or end with 1 is:
